casebody.data:
Timothy W. REGISTER, Appellant,
v.
STATE of Missouri, Respondent. WD 81005 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: March 5, 2019 Alexandria Shah, St. Louis, MO, Counsel for Appellant. Shaun Mackelprang, Jefferson City, MO, Counsel for Respondent. Before Division One: Cynthia L. Martin, P.J., Victor C. Howard, and Thomas H. Newton, JJ.

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Mr. Timothy W. Register appeals the Morgan County Circuit Court judgment denying an amended Rule 29.15 motion following an evidentiary hearing. For reasons stated in the memorandum provided to the parties, we affirm. Rule 84.16(b).
